flowchart TB
    N1["1. neo-execution-core: Trust boundary shows what must be proven rather than believed."]
    N2["2. Trusted base: explicit input constraints, transition rules, and output checks"]
    N3["3. Untrusted input: L2 batch | previous state root | execution parameters"]
    N4["4. Validation boundary: all inputs cross explicit validation boundaries"]
    N5["5. Replay and ordering: input and output digests bind the same context"]
    N6["6. Authority: authority comes from boundary contracts, not caller claims"]
    N7["7. External systems: callers, consumers, monitoring, and persistence layer"]
    N8["8. Observed evidence: input digest, output digest, state change, and rejection reason"]
    N1 --> N2
    N1 --> N3
    N1 --> N4
    N1 --> N5
    N1 --> N6
    N1 --> N7
    N1 --> N8
